 frühen 20. Jahrhunderts.Dieser Band bietet eine vielfältige Analyse der Ästhetisierung des Sozialen im heutigen Zeitalter visueller Medien, die im Sinne einer historischen Kultursoziologie medial-ästhetischer Praktiken weit in die Geschichte zurückreicht.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4aAvantgarde. 4aBild. 4aBildwissenschaft. 4aCultural Studies. 4aGesellschaft. 4aKultursoziologie. 4aKunst. 4aKunstsoziologie. 4aKunstwissenschaft. 4aMedien. 4aVisual Culture. 4aÄsthetik. 7aART / Criticism.2bisacsh  aAesthetics.  aArts.  aCultural Studies.  aFine Arts.  aImage.  aMedia.  aSociety.  aSociology of Art.  aSociology of Culture.  aVisual Studies.1 aFugger, Dominik, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGlauser, Andrea, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHaring, Sabine A., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHieber, Lutz, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHieber, Lutz, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aKautt, York, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLandes, Lilian, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLippl, Bodo, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMoebius, Stephan, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMoebius, Stephan, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aRudin, Dominique, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRummel-Suhrcke, Ralf, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aScherke, Katharina, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aUrban, Andreas, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabular